  <h1>Future Possibilities</h1>
    <p><img src="images/djembe1.gif" alt="African Djembe" width="90" height="58" align="middle" /><img src="images/gong.gif" alt="Balinese Gong" width="27" height="27" hspace="40" align="middle" /><img src="images/bayan.gif" alt="Indian Bayan" width="72" height="74" align="middle" /></p>
